beer.beer_description:
Witness the power of Simcoe Cryo showcased in this single hop pale ale.

Cryo hops have been cryogenically processed to seperate the lupulin (the stuff the hop heads love) from the flower.

An American pale ale that makes you feel like you’re waltzing through a pine forest.

A delicious hoppy feast for the nostrils and palate.
